Package shibboleth.model

Bussiness model classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Chunk
    A chunk is a contiguous piece of a GitFile with authorship information.
    Committer
    A committer is someone who committed to a git project.
    Contribution
    Represents a contribution to a repo by a user.
    ContributionInfo
    A class which provides information about a contribution.
    GitFile
    Represents a file of a given commit in a cloned git repository.
    GitGraph
    A (bipartite) directed graph containing users and repos and their relationship.
    RecordLink
    Represents a match between a git committer and a Github user.
    Repo
    Data class which represents a Github repository.
    SimpleRepo
    Represents a Github repo, of which we only know its name.
    SimpleUser
    Represents a Github user of which we only know his username.
    UnknownUser
    A github user, but we do not know who it is...
    User
    Data class which represents a Github user.
